  "title": "Sales Assistant Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Assist the Sales Manager in driving sales growth by supporting planning, executing, and achieving sales targets while ensuring effective team coordination and customer relationship management.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Collaborate with the Sales Manager to develop and implement sales plans that achieve business objectives</li><li>Coordinate daily sales operations to ensure seamless communication and workflow within the sales team</li><li>Lead and motivate sales staff by providing guidance and performance feedback to enhance productivity</li><li>Build and sustain strong relationships with existing and prospective customers to foster loyalty and business growth</li><li>Manage customer inquiries and negotiations promptly and professionally to resolve issues and secure sales</li><li>Prepare detailed sales reports, forecasts, and presentations to inform management decision-making</li><li>Analyze market trends and competitor activities to provide actionable insights for refining sales strategies</li><li>Ensure adherence to company policies, procedures, and sales standards to maintain operational compliance</li><li>Actively participate in sales meetings, training programs, and promotional events to support team development</li><li>Assume leadership of the sales team during the Sales Manager’s absence to maintain continuity and performance</li></ul>",
